summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4236 for the improvement of 50th Avenue South from Flethcer Street to Barton Place; by grading and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 50341, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
